      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex max-lg:flex-col lg:justify-evenly gap-5 items-center mt-20 lg:pb-[200px] pb-20 font-sans-instrument">
      <div class="relative max-md:w-full">
        <Image src={kitImage1} alt={"kitImage1"} class="w-full bg-cover rounded-xl"/>
        <p class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-white font-normal text-2xl leading-8">Secure support where it matters most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-5">
        <div class="relative">
          <Image src={kitImage2} alt={"kitImage1"} class='rounded-xl'/>
          <p class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-white font-normal text-2xl leading-8">Reduce slip risks instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <Image src={kitImage3} alt={"kitImage1"} class='rounded-xl'/>
          <p class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-white font-normal text-2xl leading-8">Slim, sturdy, and slip-resistant.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-5 max-md:w-full">
        <div class="relative">
          <Image src={kitImage4} alt={"kitImage1"} class="w-full bg-cover rounded-xl"/>
          <p class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-white font-normal text-2xl leading-8">Invisible protection, powerful grip.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <Image src={kitImage5} alt={"kitImage1"} class="w-full bg-cover rounded-xl"/>
          <p class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-white font-normal text-2xl leading-8">Assess today, prevent tomorrowâ€™s falls.</p>
